    javafx.fxml.Initializable
    public class MainController
extends java.lang.Object
implements javafx.fxml.Initializable
    MainController is called by main and begins the app, buttons and inital user input will be handled by this class. Run time errors when adding non integer values, fixed in the modifyPart, modifyProduct, addProducts methods
